                          <amp-img srcset="/images/1080p_webUI/1080p_Settings_Features_Nightvision.jpg 100w, /images/1080p_webUI/1080p_Settings_Features_Nightvision.png 1500w" width="1371" height="949" layout="responsive" class="shadow"></amp-img>
